content: Darkstep是Drum and Bass的一种子风格，特点是快速的鼓点和暗黑氛围，其发展受到Dark Ambient、Industrial和Hardcore音乐的影响。
contentEn: Darkstep is characterised by fast drums and a general dark mood, drawing influences from dark ambient, industrial and hardcore music.
